00:01:01,750 --> 00:01:03,050
It's the smell.

3
00:01:03,780 --> 00:01:05,320
The smell of death.

4
00:01:06,920 --> 00:01:09,550
This place reeks of it even at this very moment.

5
00:01:19,800 --> 00:01:23,170
Do it now. Shoot! Hurry up and shoot!

6
00:01:23,800 --> 00:01:24,940
Do you want to die?

7
00:01:37,150 --> 00:01:38,220
Shoot!

8
00:01:38,580 --> 00:01:41,650
Shoot him now! Don't care about me! Just hurry up and shoot!

9
00:02:03,740 --> 00:02:05,180
Seal all the entrances and take the stairs.

10
00:02:21,630 --> 00:02:22,830
You have no idea...

11
00:02:23,660 --> 00:02:24,760
how much I missed you.

12
00:02:33,000 --> 00:02:36,340
You got shot, so take off your mask and say hello.

13
00:02:37,010 --> 00:02:39,310
Where are your manners? Let's see what you've got.

14
00:02:40,040 --> 00:02:41,910
I'll aim properly this time.

15
00:02:42,650 --> 00:02:45,320
I'm impressed. You win.

16
00:02:45,520 --> 00:02:47,980
If you admit that you lost, get down on your knees.

17
00:02:47,980 --> 00:02:50,120
Why weren't you able to do anything...

18
00:02:50,620 --> 00:02:52,820
when your mom died right in front of your eyes?

19
00:02:54,190 --> 00:02:55,430
Who are you?

20
00:02:58,500 --> 00:03:01,160
Do you even remember how your mom died?

21
00:03:01,900 --> 00:03:04,900
"Mom. Mom."

22
00:03:05,000 --> 00:03:06,440
Mom.

23
00:03:07,340 --> 00:03:08,970
Mom.

24
00:03:10,140 --> 00:03:11,570
You son of a gun.

25
00:03:11,570 --> 00:03:13,680
I remember it very clearly.

26
00:03:13,840 --> 00:03:17,350
You cried like a little baby in front of your dying mother.

27
00:03:17,710 --> 00:03:19,020
Do me a favor.

28
00:03:21,320 --> 00:03:23,120
Don't bother putting on those handcuffs.

29
00:03:23,990 --> 00:03:25,290
and make a run for it.

30
00:03:27,890 --> 00:03:28,990
I urge you to.

31
00:03:43,440 --> 00:03:46,340
(SWAT)

32
00:03:52,350 --> 00:03:53,750
Do not forget...

33
00:03:54,850 --> 00:03:56,090
my last words.

34
00:03:56,190 --> 00:03:57,420
Don't use your energy to talk and stay awake.

35
00:03:57,420 --> 00:03:58,420
You must find it.

36
00:03:59,820 --> 00:04:00,920
Don't forget...

37
00:04:04,960 --> 00:04:06,130
the meadow...

38
00:04:09,870 --> 00:04:10,930
(SWAT)

39
00:04:26,850 --> 00:04:28,120
The meadow...

40
00:04:29,320 --> 00:04:30,490
The meadow?

41
00:05:09,590 --> 00:05:12,060
He fell from the roof. Send units to the back door!

42
00:05:19,270 --> 00:05:20,570
The target is at the back door on the first floor.

43
00:05:20,770 --> 00:05:22,170
He's in a SWAT officer's uniform.

44
00:05:22,370 --> 00:05:23,470
To the first floor.

45
00:05:23,670 --> 00:05:26,740
The suspect is dressed as one of us. All officers, take off your mask.

46
00:06:25,340 --> 00:06:28,370
We lost them. The target and Detective Dong.

47
00:06:31,470 --> 00:06:32,740
I'll take responsibility.

48
00:06:33,040 --> 00:06:34,140
Responsibility?

49
00:06:34,440 --> 00:06:35,650
Just know this.

50
00:06:36,080 --> 00:06:38,410
No one will be able to take responsibility for this.

51
00:06:39,020 --> 00:06:40,480
Even our dismissal from the force...

52
00:06:41,050 --> 00:06:42,790
won't be enough to avoid the back blast.

53
