00:57:40,990 --> 00:57:42,160
Lee Su Hyeon.

780
00:57:43,430 --> 00:57:44,530
Park Hwan Uk.

781
00:57:45,070 --> 00:57:46,270
Yoo Chang Hoon.

782
00:57:46,770 --> 00:57:48,030
Kim Sang Soo.

783
00:57:49,300 --> 00:57:50,440
Oh Gyeong Hoon.

784
00:57:51,140 --> 00:57:52,310
Jo In Hye.

785
00:57:52,970 --> 00:57:54,210
Jang Seok Chan.

786
00:57:55,810 --> 00:57:58,250
Lee Geon Woo. Park Seong Min.

787
00:57:59,110 --> 00:58:00,510
Lee Sang Hoon.

788
00:58:00,880 --> 00:58:02,180
Kim Tae Hyeon.

789
00:58:03,080 --> 00:58:04,320
Lee Jun Woo.

790
00:58:06,690 --> 00:58:08,260
These 17 people...

791
00:58:09,190 --> 00:58:11,090
died because of you, Dad.

792
00:58:13,990 --> 00:58:15,500
They died because of us.

793
00:58:18,430 --> 00:58:20,400
Dad, I know you can't say anything.

794
00:58:22,570 --> 00:58:24,600
And I know you guys can't hear this.

795
00:58:33,150 --> 00:58:34,880
But I'm still very sorry.

796
00:58:37,680 --> 00:58:41,090
He loved justifying his murders, but that's not how he kills anymore.

797
00:58:41,220 --> 00:58:44,320
- The innocent will be crucified. - On behalf of the sinner.

798
00:58:44,490 --> 00:58:46,330
His purpose was to murder people.

799
00:58:46,330 --> 00:58:47,830
Chun Ki Soo is the connection.

800
00:58:47,930 --> 00:58:49,000
Who are you?

801
00:58:49,160 --> 00:58:52,070
Your savior. The person who can save your son.

802
00:58:52,170 --> 00:58:54,370
- Chun Ki Soo disappeared. - There isn't a single trace.

803
00:58:54,530 --> 00:58:57,300
He was after the Eraser.

804
00:58:57,300 --> 00:58:59,610
- What? - I saw the scar on his right arm.

805
00:58:59,840 --> 00:59:01,780
- Who was that? - You were the Eraser.

806
00:59:02,110 --> 00:59:04,580
You were at Shimbae City 20 years ago!

